column2: SELECT m.recno, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra_sdss, o.dec AS dec_sdss, o.mode, o.clean, o.fiberMag_u, o.fiberMagErr_u, o.fiberMag_g, o.fiberMagErr_g, o.fiberMag_r, o.fiberMagErr_r, o.fiberMag_i, o.fiberMagErr_i, o.fiberMag_z, o.fiberMagErr_z, s.z , s.zErr , s.zWarning, s.class , s.subClass, s.velDisp , s.velDispErr into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.SyCATv1# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON n.objid = o.objid
